      <title>德国林德纳敦促欧盟取消内燃机汽车淘汰日期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/germany-s-lindner-urges-eu-to-drop-combustion-engine-end-date</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 敦促欧盟放弃在短短十年内逐步淘汰内燃机的目标。]]></description>
