    <item>
      <title>南非希望通过签证改革吸引印度、中国游客</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/south-africa-seeks-to-woo-india-china-tourists-with-visa-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非计划在数日内放宽对印度和中国游客的签证规定，以吸引这两个世界人口最多的国家的游客，因为他们一直被繁文缛节所困扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/south-africa-seeks-to-woo-india-china-tourists-with-visa-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 14:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯对拜登推动对未实现收益征税保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/harris-goes-quiet-on-biden-s-push-to-tax-unrealized-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯对民主党对未实现投资收益征税的提议保持沉默——这让人怀疑她会在多大程度上推动民主党提高亿万富翁税收的关键举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/harris-goes-quiet-on-biden-s-push-to-tax-unrealized-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 14:35:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗在首次金砖国家峰会上展示与俄罗斯的“战略”关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/iran-showcases-strategic-russia-ties-at-its-first-brics-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安在金砖国家峰会上会见俄罗斯总统普京时，称伊朗与俄罗斯的关系是“战略性的”。这是伊朗首次以正式成员身份出席金砖国家峰会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/iran-showcases-strategic-russia-ties-at-its-first-brics-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 14:33:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nubank 首席执行官 Velez 表示，Milei 领导下，Nubank 将重新审视阿根廷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/nubank-taking-new-look-at-argentina-under-milei-ceo-velez-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nu Holdings Ltd. 首席执行官戴维·维莱斯 (David Velez) 表示，这家金融科技公司正在重新评估阿根廷的前景，整个拉丁美洲都在支持阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 的成功。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/nubank-taking-new-look-at-argentina-under-milei-ceo-velez-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 14:20:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼负责人称朝鲜军队已抵达俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/us-confirms-north-korean-troops-are-in-russia-to-back-its-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀称，有证据表明朝鲜正在向俄罗斯派遣军队，这导致朝鲜军队被派往乌克兰作战的可能性“非常非常大”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/us-confirms-north-korean-troops-are-in-russia-to-back-its-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 14:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北卡罗来纳州参议员蒂利斯表示特朗普将赢得摇摆州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/senator-tillis-says-trump-will-win-swing-state-north-carolina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党参议员汤姆·蒂利斯预测，前总统唐纳德·特朗普将在遭受风暴袭击的北卡罗来纳州赢得总统大选，尽管民意调查显示，这场竞争越来越激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/senator-tillis-says-trump-will-win-swing-state-north-carolina</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 13:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国外交官布林肯前往沙特阿拉伯，呼吁以色列缓解与伊朗有关的冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/us-diplomat-blinken-heads-to-saudi-arabia-after-urging-israel-to-ease-conflicts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登的高级外交官与沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼举行会谈，讨论在加沙和黎巴嫩达成停火的努力，以争取地区支持推动和平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/us-diplomat-blinken-heads-to-saudi-arabia-after-urging-israel-to-ease-conflicts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 08:05:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平与莫迪举行边界协议达成两年来首次会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/xi-modi-to-hold-first-talks-in-two-years-after-border-consensus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周早些时候，中国国家主席习近平在 2022 年以来的首次双边会晤中对印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪表示，两国应加强关系，妥善处理分歧。此前，两国已缓解了长达四年的边境僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/xi-modi-to-hold-first-talks-in-two-years-after-border-consensus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 03:12:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦财政部长认为中国债务谈判“令人鼓舞”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/pakistan-says-debt-reprofile-talks-with-china-are-encouraging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦财政部长表示，巴基斯坦关于延长“一带一路”贷款期限的请求得到了中国的积极回应，这意味着过去深陷高昂借贷成本的国家可能将获得更多喘息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/pakistan-says-debt-reprofile-talks-with-china-are-encouraging</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 19:08:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
